              {
                "id": "6c93b198-b9fb-4677-b028-281e607c01ef",
                "orderNumber": 3,
                "title": null,
                "content": "Seems like a crazy question for Jesus to ask the guy. Doesn’t it?",
                "isLocked": false,
                "contentFormat": "markdown"
              },
              {
                "id": "f0649125-912b-4639-bb9e-57d81e782d06",
                "orderNumber": 4,
                "title": null,
                "content": "Let’s read it in context - understanding Jesus FULLY understands the human condition.",
                "isLocked": false,
                "contentFormat": "markdown"
              },
              {
                "id": "3407ea94-cf78-4b33-9a47-cde5c497aef7",
                "orderNumber": 5,
                "title": null,
                "content": "There are lots of other people with conditions like his there. This man’s condition had become his identity.",
                "isLocked": false,
                "contentFormat": "markdown"
              },
              {
                "id": "b5714867-0e5a-4cad-88d3-fa07dd7d4e2f",
                "orderNumber": 6,
                "title": null,
                "content": "This man’s disability had become his excuse.",
                "isLocked": false,
                "contentFormat": "markdown"
              },
              {
                "id": "a369fab7-69e5-4cee-b202-76c3d3e9a954",
                "orderNumber": 7,
                "title": null,
                "content": "Was it the water that healed any of them?",
                "isLocked": false,
                "contentFormat": "markdown"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
